        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=76406&amp;TOPIC_ID=8886&amp;FORUM_ID=2&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=General+Discussions&amp;Topic_Title=Mind+wrack+changed+%2D+good+and+bad+news&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Far as I'm conserned it's the final nail in the coffin for a spell that started out with so much potential, but got nerfed so hard lvl 12 n00bs wouldn't use it.  Range was lowered so you can't feed mana to casters if they're hiding from AoE.  Mana Drain was increased to 1200 to make sure the mobs would go oom faster.  But that was changed the moment verant realized that people were using it as a mana seive.  So now they've simply removed the last bit of usefullness from it, to make it an instatap, like our lifetap line, but yet let the recource remain a DoT. this keeps multiple people from tapping a mob at the same time to keep it from going oom.</P><P>/mourn decent luclin spell, I'll miss you</P><P>Reepr<BR>Warlock of Lanys<BR><Sigil><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
